text: Dubovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Nizhnebaltachevsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 31 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 21 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 2 km from Nizhnebaltachevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Dubovka, Republic of Bashkortostan
